      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable driver who doesn't mind a bit of character. While the engine and transmission are functional and have been regularly serviced, the car shows its age with several noticeable scuffs on the bumpers, a few small door dings, and some thinning paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. It has been a dependable commuter, but a new owner should expect to address these minor cosmetic issues and keep up with routine maintenance to ensure its continued longevity.",
