    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, dependable ride without any fuss. I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and well-loved, so it's totally ready for your next adventure. If you're looking for a great deal on a car that still has plenty of life and spirit, this is the one! Feel free to message me if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates and fresh RTABs for improved lateral stability. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior displays minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronicity and throttle response remain sharp, offering an authentic analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
