      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term value. This example retains its aesthetic integrity and mechanical precision, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. With a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it stands as a premier choice for the discerning driver who demands both excellence and dependability in their next automotive investment.",
      "price": 36500.0,
