      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and is still in wonderful shape! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it over the years, and it still drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something dependable and ready for your next big road trip, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
