    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46). At its heart is the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure peak torque delivery. This example features the sought-after 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory M-tuned limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a vital preventive measure for this chassis. The suspension benefits from refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are top-tier, making this a perfect candidate for the purist driver.",
